ched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-05T18:10:05Z to 2025-06-05T18:34:05Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-05 18:10:05+00:00 to 2025-06-05 18:34:05+00:00"}, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "emailservice-1", "shippingservice-1", "recommendationservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "recommendationservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["recommendationservice-0", "frontend-0", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-2", "adservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "checkoutservice-0", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2", "checkoutservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-0", "adservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "cartservice-0", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "shippingservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "redis-cart-0", "cartservice-1", "adservice-2", "shippingservice-1", "recommendationservice-0"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的日志数据，我对故障进行了分析。从日志中可以看到，所有的错误都来自frontend服务，并且都指向同一个问题：无法连接到IP地址为10.233.46.196:7070的目标服务。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"connection refused\", \"port\", \"Unavailable\", \"rpc error\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"端口配置错误导致连接被拒绝，所有frontend实例都无法连接到cartservice的7070端口\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: connect: connection refused\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结：**\n\n1. **错误模式识别**：所有日志都显示相同的连接错误模式，指向同一个目标IP和端口（10.233.46.196:7070）\n\n2. **关键发现**：\n   - 所有frontend实例（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）都报告相同的连接问题\n   - 错误涉及购物车相关操作：添加商品到购物车、获取购物车信息、完成订单\n   - 目标服务应该是cartservice（基于业务逻辑推断）\n\n3. **根因判断**：这是一个典型的端口配置错误问题\n   - 特征：`connection refused` + 固定的目标IP端口\n   - 被调方服务（cartservice）可能配置了错误的端口号或服务未正确启动\n   - 调用方（frontend）健康但无法连接到目标服务\n\n4. **证据强度**：所有30条错误日志都指向同一个问题，出现频率高，具有明确的模式一致性。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的trace数据分析，我发现了明确的故障根因。以下是详细分析：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"cartservice->unavailable\", \"frontend->cartservice\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService连接被拒绝：'connection error: desc = transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: connect: connection refused'，出现次数超过3000次\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService/GetProduct操作延迟从正常11-12秒增加到异常13-14秒，延迟增加约20%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PlaceOrder操作因CartService不可用而失败，正常耗时约150秒，异常时降至5-7秒（Fast Fail模式）\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 根因分析总结：\n\n**主要根因：CartService完全不可用**\n- CartService（IP: 10.233.46.196:7070）出现连接被拒绝错误\n- 该错误影响了所有依赖CartService的服务：Frontend、CheckoutService\n- 错误传播路径：CartService → Frontend/CheckoutService → 前端用户\n\n**次要影响：ProductCatalogService延迟增加**\n- GetProduct操作延迟增加约20%，可能是系统负载增加导致的连锁反应\n\n**故障特征：**\n- CartService完全宕机（连接被拒绝）\n- 依赖服务进入Fast Fail模式（PlaceOrder操作耗时从150秒降至5-7秒）\n- 前端返回大量500错误（HTTP status code: 500）", "metric_analysis_findings": "Based on the metric data analysis for the fault period from 2025-06-05T18:10:05Z to 2025-06-05T18:34:05Z, I can identify several key anomalies. Let me analyze the findings:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio and server_error_ratio across all frontend pods (frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2) with median error ratios rising from 0.0 to 27-28%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: error_ratio 0.0→28.08%, frontend-1: 0.0→28.48%, frontend-2: 0.0→27.88%; server_error_ratio shows similar increases\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"High client_error_ratio and error_ratio in p99 values across all shippingservice pods (40-49% error rates) indicating downstream service failures\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-0: p99 error_ratio 40.72%, shippingservice-1: 41.15%, shippingservice-2: 49.56%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Severe rrt_max and rrt degradation with p99 values showing 18-25x increase in response times, combined with elevated error ratios\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-2: rrt_max from 11121.12 to 2542166.8 (228x increase), cartservice-0: rrt_max from 35080.0 to 2054997.75 (58x increase)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"High server_error_ratio in p99 values (12.81%) and significant rrt_max degradation indicating Redis performance issues\",\n      \"evidence\": \"redis-cart-0: p99 server_error_ratio 12.81%, rrt_max p99 from 84484.32 to 1315.9 (significant degradation)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**Analysis Summary:**\nThe fault appears to be a cascading failure starting with the cartservice and redis components. The cartservice shows extreme response time degradation (rrt_max increases by 18-25x), which likely caused the high error rates observed in the frontend service. The shippingservice also shows high client error rates, suggesting it's affected by downstream service failures. The redis-cart-0 instance shows error rates and response time issues, indicating potential Redis performance problems that could be contributing to the cartservice failures."}
